### 4.4 Registrar Máquina
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MiBoundary123

--MiBoundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ver"

registrar_maquina
--MiBoundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="empresa_idempresa"

{{id_empresa}}
--MiBoundary123
